column5: Marty dont you be leaving the country.   It,s all most time for,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,   SQUISH THE FISH.  I,ll just add it to my collection of Bills bets.    Poor fella looks a little scared wouldnt ya say. I know I would, if I seen a heard of Buffalos coming at me.LOL
Game time, got to go. History in the making.
You know Lawyers don't work Sundays Brian...
What the heck happen.  Miami played a great game. Bills on the other hand,well,maybe they werent expecting this kind of fan base and were in ahhhh.LOL  Now I got to send a Canadian fin to marty.
It was too warm with the roof closed Brian. We made 'em feel too comfortable.

Sorry Brian, I was at Heinz Field watching the best defense in football make America's Team look pathetic.  Ten wins while playing the toughest schedule in football and despite injuries to half the team.    Not to mention a bad offense.  The Bills suck.   They really do.   Sorry.
So do the loafs,but we got to cheer on the home town boys just the same.LOL
